      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-pseo-target="h1">UUID and GUID explained — what they are and when to generate one</h1>
            <div class="tb-card tb-card-soft tb-card-note tb-card-pad-sm mt-3 mb-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
